movieclassifier.py implements machine learning classifier(s) based on movie review dataset 
from https://ai.stanford.edu/~amaas/data/sentiment/
movieclassifier.py assumes above data downloaded to D:\NLP\dataset\aclImdb

result_### files captured run results using a portion of the dataset (e.g. 12000 means 12000 reviews are used etc)

trained classfier would be saved to pickle file locally